Scanning electron micrograph of head of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Arias, new" authorityYear="2004" box="[635,769,737,756]" class="Insecta" family="Elateridae" genus="Alyma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lawlerae">
